description: Turns every vendor and tool request into a structured approval packet — cost, risk, alternatives, compliance flags, and a decision-ready owner chain — before it touches a budget holder. Keep your ERP and finance system. Replace the Google Form, the Airtable tracker, and the Slack thread nobody follows up on.
